<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+访谈记录CN-1544-1-02</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-访谈记录CN-1544-1-02</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<blockquote>
<p><strong>受访者：</strong>SCP-CN-1544-1</p>
<p><strong>采访者：</strong>思博士</p>
<p><strong>&lt;记录开始，██/██/████&gt;</strong></p>
<p><strong>思博士：</strong>关于<a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-2935">SCP-2935</a>，你都知道些什么？<br />
